---
title: Oven-Roasted Salmon with Avocado, Tangelo & Quinoa Salad
description: Citrus is the gift that keeps on giving! Its tangy fruit and zest go into this protein-packed salmon dish. Never tried tangelos? They're a delicious mix between a tangerine and a grapefruit! A citrus-scallion vinaigrette adds vibrance to nutty quinoa and zesty arugula, Luscious avocado is just the cherry on top!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/552e7e1c6ced6e9b3c8b4568.jpg
